 r←Test_028(stopFlag batchFlag);⎕TRAP;path;zipFilename;targetFolder;myZip;list2;this;list1;path2
⍝ Create a new Zip archive, add some files and then unzip it
 ⎕TRAP←(999 'C' '∘∘∘ ⍝ Deliberate error')(0 'N')
